<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我跟你說喔，<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay frames="40" />
剛才我在附近散步的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天空掉下來一個東西，你猜是什麼？<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然是<colour id="1" /><delay20 />復活節花冠<colour id="65535" />的方程式！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一人獨佔就太說不過去了，<delay20 />
所以我要跟你分享！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">難道<delay8 />還有其他的嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要<delay20 />找遍島上所有地方才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />你包包裡<delay8 />
還滿多東西的嘛。<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，<delay20 />等你減輕包包的重量後，再來找我吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要趁我<delay8 />還沒改變主意的時候來喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個啊，<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay frames="30" />
我撿到了一個
滿有趣的東西耶！<pageBreak /><anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你問我撿到了什麼？<delay20 />那就是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<colour id="1" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節包包<colour id="65535" />的方程式！<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經抄成<delay8 />給自己看的筆記了，<delay20 />
這個就給你吧。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay8 />接下來就要努力<delay20 />
收集蛋來當材料了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我是這麼想的啦，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是你的口袋已經滿了，<delay8 />放不進去呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你先騰出口袋的空間，<delay20 />再來找我吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我今天一整天<delay8 />都會帶在身上的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>